@startuml
actor 参与者 as Buddy
participant "小程序端" as Frontend
participant "服务端 (syncPostStatus/settlePost)" as Backend
database "MySQL数据库" as DB

' 提交证据部分
Buddy -> Frontend : 上传证据内容
Frontend -> Backend : POST /api/posts/:id/evidence
activate Backend
Backend -> DB : INSERT INTO evidences
DB --> Backend : 写入成功
Backend --> Frontend : 返回 HTTP 201
deactivate Backend

' 异步/触发式 状态流转与结算
note over Backend, DB: 满足条件且过了评价截止时间时触发结算
Backend -> DB : 获取数据库连接并开启事务 (BEGIN)
activate DB
DB -> DB : UPDATE posts SET status = '已完成'
DB -> DB : UPDATE users SET points = points + reward (发布者)
DB -> DB : UPDATE users SET points = points + reward (所有搭子)
DB --> Backend : 事务提交 (COMMIT)
deactivate DB

Backend -> DB : UPDATE users SET completionRate = ... (重算完成率)
@enduml